sing /sɪŋ/

(singing,sang,sung,sings) 

1. V-T/V-I When you sing , you make musical sounds with your voice, usually producing words that fit a tune. 唱 

例： I can't sing. 我不会唱歌。 

例： I sing about love most of the time. 我大部分时间都在歌唱爱情。 

例： They were all singing the same song. 他们在唱同一首歌。 

